## cloneRawRequest()

Clones the raw Request object from a HonoRequest. Works even after the request body has been consumed by validators or HonoRequest methods.

```ts twoslash
import { Hono } from 'hono'
const app = new Hono()

import { cloneRawRequest } from 'hono/request'
